Package: sitingclass
Type: Package
Title: Siting classification of Norwegian weather stations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pierre-Marie Lefeuvre
Maintainer: Pierre-Marie Lefeuvre <pierre.marie.lefeuvre@met.no>
Description: The package sitingclass evaluates the exposure of weather stations for specific sensors from digital elevation models. The package is currently designed for Met usage only, due to data restrictions.
URL: https://gitlab.met.no/pierreml/sitingclass
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
